text:
The other day I was working on something in the REPL, and pressed "up" on my keyboard to get the last thing I typed, and _this_ block of code appeared:
```Builder(ctx) do builder
   entry = BasicBlock(sum, "entry", ctx)
   position!(builder, entry)

   tmp = add!(builder, parameters(sum)[1], parameters(sum)[2], "tmp")
   ret!(builder, tmp)
end```
I did not write, nor include, this code snippet in the REPL (in any open terminals). I'm curious how this could happen, does this look familiar to anyone?
